OL,3,CShoes found in search for missing teen
OL,4,Cnot seen in a week
OL,6,FA pair of shoes has been found in the
OL,7,Fsearch for a missing 14-year-old boy
OL,8,Fin Barnstaple.
OL,10,FTaylor Charlton was last seen at
OL,11,Faround 10.40pm on Friday 8 May near a
OL,12,FTesco store in the Seven Brethren
OL,13,Farea, Devon and Cornwall Police have
OL,14,Fsaid.
OL,16,FThe teenager is around 5ft 8in tall,
OL,17,Fof muscular build, with dark brown
OL,18,Fhair and a moustache and was last seen
OL,19,Fwearing a bright blue fitted top,
OL,20,Fjeans and bright blue Nike shoes,
OL,21,Fofficers added.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/7
