PN,43302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1779098804
OL,3,CShoes found in search for missing teen
OL,4,Cnot seen in a week
OL,6,FDetectives and specialist police teams
OL,7,Fhave been carrying out extensive
OL,8,Fenquiries in the North Devon town.
OL,10,FThe shoes are believed to belong to
OL,11,FTaylor and were found near to the
OL,12,FRiver Taw in the Tarka Trail area
OL,13,Fbetween Sticklepath and Bickington.
OL,15,FThe 14-year-old was reported as
OL,16,Fmissing on the early evening of
OL,17,FSaturday 9 May.
OL,19,FPolice say they are keeping all
OL,20,Favenues of enquiry open.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,434,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1779098804
OL,3,CShoes found in search for missing teen
OL,4,Cnot seen in a week
OL,6,FThe force's theory that Taylor may
OL,7,Fhave gone into the water has meant
OL,8,Fthat police searches have focused on
OL,9,Fthis area first.
OL,11,FSector Inspector Andy Wills, from
OL,12,FDevon and Cornwall Police, said:
OL,13,F"Detectives are keeping an open
OL,14,Finvestigative mindset in our efforts
OL,15,Fto find Taylor.
OL,17,F"A hypothesis that Taylor may have
OL,18,Fentered the River Taw is currently
OL,19,Fbeing prioritised in our lines of
OL,20,Fenquiry. Our searches are currently
OL,21,Ffocussing on this area.
OL,26,@uD@AOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,434,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1779098804
OL,3,CShoes found in search for missing teen
OL,4,Cnot seen in a week
OL,6,F"We are asking the public to help us
OL,7,Fwith this by avoiding the search area.
OL,8,FIn particular, any activity on the
OL,9,Fwater could significantly disrupt the
OL,10,Fsearch operation and put you and
OL,11,Fmembers of the emergency services at
OL,12,Frisk.
OL,14,F"We would also like to remind members
OL,15,Fof the public that drone flights are
OL,16,Fprohibited in the area while searches
OL,17,Fare ongoing.
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,434,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1779098804
OL,3,CShoes found in search for missing teen
OL,4,Cnot seen in a week
OL,6,F"All of the search activity is being
OL,7,Fdirected by accredited police search
OL,8,Fadvisers, who are defining search
OL,9,Fareas in consultation with colleagues
OL,10,Fincluding HM Coastguard. The public
OL,11,Fshould expect to see focussed search
OL,12,Factivity around the River Taw.
OL,14,F"I recognise how much the community
OL,15,Fwants to help to find Taylor. If you
OL,16,Fare out looking, please take care and
OL,17,Favoid putting yourself at risk. This
OL,18,Fincludes entering unsafe buildings or
OL,19,Fgoing near the water.
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,434,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1779098804
OL,3,CShoes found in search for missing teen
OL,4,Cnot seen in a week
OL,6,F"If you become aware of an area that
OL,7,Fyou think may be relevant, please pass
OL,8,Fthis information on to us.
OL,10,F"Anyone with information, including
OL,11,Fany sightings of Taylor, is asked to
OL,12,Fcall police immediately on 999 quoting
OL,13,Freference 50260117084.
OL,15,F"We also ask people avoid sharing
OL,16,Fspeculation on social media as
OL,17,Funconfirmed information can sometimes
OL,18,Fmake enquiries more challenging."
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUwD@AOUzD@aO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
